      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for the right buyer. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but offers straightforward value as basic transportation, a project car, or a dependable spare. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overpaying, this is a compelling option priced to sell.",
