    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project candidate with strong old-school character and a surprisingly composed drivetrain. Starts, runs, and moves, with the kind of analog feel enthusiasts appreciate. Shows cosmetic wear and needs attention as expected, but the platform has good bones for someone wanting an affordable driver-to-project or weekend wrenching build. A great entry point for a buyer who values mechanical simplicity, usable parts, and room to improve.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Rough around the edges, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real personality\u2014the kind of machine that still turns an ordinary drive into something memorable. It has the honest, well-lived character of a vehicle that\u2019s been part of real adventures, and for the next owner, that means opportunity: a practical runabout, a budget-friendly set of wheels, or the perfect canvas for a hands-on project. If you appreciate charm over pretense and want something with presence, potential, and a price that leaves room to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with real value for the budget-conscious buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it offers a practical opportunity for someone seeking dependable basic transportation, a project car, or a low-cost second vehicle. Priced to reflect condition and presented with full transparency, it\u2019s a chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point from a seller you can trust.",
      "price": 5995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a project to tinker with? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner with plenty of potential for the right buyer. Great if you need something affordable, want a parts car, or enjoy bringing a vehicle back to life. Priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019m happy to chat openly about it so you know exactly what you\u2019re getting.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong runner with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Engine starts up, pulls cleanly, and the drivetrain does what it should. Suspension and chassis feel composed for an older vehicle, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great affordable driver or weekend project. Cosmetic wear and age-related blemishes are present, but the core package is there for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending big money. Priced to move and well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
